title: Marimba Solist Collection
description:
Here are several CD&#039;s of percussion soloists playing Marimba solos and a few duets.

Abe, Keiko - Marimba Fantasy - 128kbps
Ford, Mark - Polaris - 128kbps
Goulart, Gilmar - The World of Marimba - 320kbps
Howarth, Gifford - Rosewood Resonance - 128kbps
Kite, Rebecca - Prism - 128kbps
Lattanzi, Filippo - Fields - 320kbps
Moyer - Something Old... Something New - 256kbps
Mycka, Katarzyna - Marimba Dance - 320kbps
Mycka, Katarzyna - Marimba Sculpture - 320kbps
Westlake, Nigel - Onomatopoeia - 256kbps
Zeltsman, Nancy - See Ya Thursday - 256kbps

Marimba music is hard to come by in torrents or P2P networks, so if you have anything to add to this collection, please share!

I also added some various songs for marimba, or marimba with ensemble.  I have several anonymous :P songs as well.     ENJOY THE MARIMBA HAPPINESS
